lt=\"rcf 4\" title src=\"/static/4346ad4d0f0a34b7a561c7523181a6ef/04a72/rcf-4.png\" srcset=\"/static/4346ad4d0f0a34b7a561c7523181a6ef/6a467/rcf-4.png 210w,\n/static/4346ad4d0f0a34b7a561c7523181a6ef/635b1/rcf-4.png 420w,\n/static/4346ad4d0f0a34b7a561c7523181a6ef/04a72/rcf-4.png 840w,\n/static/4346ad4d0f0a34b7a561c7523181a6ef/c6d2c/rcf-4.png 1260w,\n/static/4346ad4d0f0a34b7a561c7523181a6ef/3bcc7/rcf-4.png 1270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 840px) 100vw, 840px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n<p class=\"caption\">A demonstration of the Progressive Web App on iPhone</p>\n\n  <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/cae60128591b3cf3bd629166c16949ad/3bcc7/rcf-5.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n  \n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 840px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 59.84251968503938%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\">\n      <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"rcf 5\" title src=\"/static/cae60128591b3cf3bd629166c16949ad/04a72/rcf-5.png\" srcset=\"/static/cae60128591b3cf3bd629166c16949ad/6a467/rcf-5.png 210w,\n/static/cae60128591b3cf3bd629166c16949ad/635b1/rcf-5.png 420w,\n/static/cae60128591b3cf3bd629166c16949ad/04a72/rcf-5.png 840w,\n/static/cae60128591b3cf3bd629166c16949ad/c6d2c/rcf-5.png 1260w,\n/static/cae60128591b3cf3bd629166c16949ad/3bcc7/rcf-5.png 1270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 840px) 100vw, 840px\">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n<p class=\"caption\">Banner that was used for Product Hunt</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"I Just Launched v1.0 of My Rental Cash Flow Calculator App","date":"A